Alexandria cemeteries, summaries of interviews concerning Seay Chapel United Methodist Church

The Alexandria Cemeteries Historic District is located at the end of Cemetery Street in Alexandria, TN. The cemeteries are located behind an extant historic African-American church, Seay Chapel United Methodist Church. The cemeteries include: Alexandria City Cemetery for African Americans, and East View White Cemetery.
